OL,3,CEx-partner admits murdering 'one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind' mum
OL,6,FThe ex-partner of a woman who was
OL,7,F"stabbed multiple times" has admitted
OL,8,Fher murder.
OL,10,FMichele Kennedy, 55, was found with
OL,11,Fserious stab wounds after the attack,
OL,12,Fon Manchester Road in Woolston,
OL,13,FWarrington, on Monday 13 October 2025.
OL,15,FOfficers attended the scene and found
OL,16,FMichele outside the residential
OL,17,Faddress, and she was taken to Aintree
OL,18,FHospital by air ambulance.
OL,20,FThe mum died five days later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
