FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771878798
OL,3,CEx-partner admits murdering 'one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind' mum
OL,6,FHer former partner, Gavin Shaw, 61,
OL,7,Fwas initially charged with attempted
OL,8,Fmurder, but following her death it was
OL,9,Fchanged to murder.
OL,11,FHe appeared at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,12,Fon Monday 23 February, where he
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty
OL,15,FMichele's family described her as a
OL,16,F"much-loved daughter, mother, sister,
OL,17,Fauntie, and nana" who was "one of a
OL,18,Fkind".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771878798
OL,3,CEx-partner admits murdering 'one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind' mum
OL,6,FThey said: "She was a larger-than-life
OL,7,Fcharacter who would leave a lasting
OL,8,Fimpression on all that met her, who
OL,9,Fwould help anyone, was beautiful,
OL,10,Fstrong, fearless and one of a kind.
OL,12,F"The loss of her life has left a
OL,13,Fmassive hole in our family, and we
OL,14,Fknow that her friends and colleagues
OL,15,Fwho were involved in her life will
OL,16,Ffeel the same.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771878798
OL,3,CEx-partner admits murdering 'one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind' mum
OL,6,F"We would like to offer our extended
OL,7,Fthanks to all the emergency services
OL,8,Fthat attended the scene and any kind
OL,9,Fperson that tried to help. We will
OL,10,Fmiss her very much."
OL,12,FFollowing the guilty plea, Detective
OL,13,FInspector Eleanor Atkinson, who led
OL,14,Fthe investigation said:"This was an
OL,15,Fexceptionally traumatic incident for
OL,16,Fall those involved, especially
OL,17,FMichele's family, neighbours and the
OL,18,Femergency services who tried to help
OL,19,Fher following the attack.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1771878798
OL,3,CEx-partner admits murdering 'one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind' mum
OL,6,F"While nothing can ever be done to
OL,7,Fbring her back, I do hope that the
OL,8,Fconclusion of this case will bring her
OL,9,Ffamily some closure.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts remain with Michele's
OL,12,Ffamily and friends at this time, and
OL,13,Fwe would like to thank them for their
OL,14,Fcooperation throughout our
OL,15,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@OO]
